<br>
Weapon delay has nothing to do with backstab delay<br>
<br>
Haste spells (including bard songs) have never affected my backstab delay from what I could see<br>
<br>
Haste items have reduced my delay (sped up my backstabs) noticably. and the better the haste, the faster the backstabs.<br>
<br>
and unhasted backstabs have the same delay as Pick Pocket, Sense Heading, etc.<br>
<br>
again, just my 2cp<br>
